name: Penicillins
title: Penicillins
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values includes select antibiotics that are Penicillins . Including oral and IV formulations.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who are on Penicillins antibiotics),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes that represent Penicillins antibiotics  and any that has the ingredients as  Penicillins: Natural penicillins (penicillin G, penicillin V), Aminopenicillins (amoxicillin, ampicillin), Penicillinase-resistant penicillins (dicloxicillin, oxacillin, naficillin), Anti-pseudomonal penicillins (piperacillin, ticarcillin),),(Exclusion Criteria: Otic, Topical and Ophthalmic formulation. Excludes carbenicillin (no human prescribable form in RxNav0.)
